metadata.name: Rose Queen
metadata.description:
The Rose Queen has begun creating her life story. 
She has made her mind,  
She has stepped into the path of liberation with courage.  
But with an apprehensive look, 
she hides her face behind the red flowers  
looking for an opening to see the light  
Rose Queen is waitingâ€¦  
Her soul yearns for touching freedom  
And she thinks to herself  
when all the windows would open to light  
when her liberation will start  
when she can come out of the roses?
